title: SIXTEEN | Official Attendance & Event Extras
body_text:
I don't even like saying "event" anymore because ECD is so much more than that, especially now.
When your best friends' kids are runnin' around with smiles equally as big as ours - not to mention numerous other family members in attendance (including my 2 year-old nephew).. this is the life, and it's wonderful.
Thank you, everyone!
